title: Sinkholes, Part 1
itunes:title: Sinkholes, Part 1
description:
In this episode of Stuff to Blow Your Mind, Robert and Joe explore the science and history of sinkholes. How have these impressive geographic features impacted our world, and what can they reveal about the past?
